video.title: Highlight: Twitch Plays (Viewers play/Chat plays) "Super Mario 64" on a real N64 console, type "!help" to learn how to play

commenter.name: neko_ni_naritai
commenter.bio: Aloooo, poisíaaaa uwu. Soy el Neko y pues me gusta mucho los juegos obvio; juego una gran variedad. Siempre trataré de estar atento al chat y que la pasen genial! ✨ (ESP/ENG)

message.body: @neko_ni_naritai Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (133 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive:

message.body: @AttemptedNerder Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (133 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive:

message.body: @amidgetontheinternet Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (133 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case
